        "TileImage": "$($repository 413cab9e-838c-4412-aadb-8c6f14098730).Image",
        "Description": "Hello again Mr. Agent 47. We need you to take care of a loose end. Do this and you are one step closer in getting your precious Diana back. Mr. Lance Bennet has left his earpiece behind in Dubai and now is burned. Get to him before he can burn us. He and his girlfriend  Ramza El-Dia are on Haven Island. We will be in touch.\r\rHint: Be sure to interrogate these 2 before you kill them.  Show Ramza a picture of Lance&apos;s body before you interrogate her. These 2  know where Diana can be found.\r\rFrom RS",
